message: /* Personal Life */The article is misleading, if you're reporting from the article then kindly read, it's written on the article only about the payment of taxes, the article is old and obsolete.. Irrelevant article against the living person should not be there.

/* Personal Life */The given article itself says that the tax was paid along with the interest. Also, the 2014 article is already obsolete, lack updates and stays irrelevant. Not removed anything but added the relevant statement.

"A demand for about ₹3.08 crore as service tax liability was raised on Samagam which was paid along with an interest of ₹80 lakh. Service tax is levied at the rate of 12.36 per cent." Available at this link- https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/Nirmal-Baba-slapped-with-%E2%82%B93.5-cr-service-tax-evasion-charge/article20730791.ece
